<section xmlns="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/dc-library" xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <prefix>§</prefix>
  <num>[25-116.01]</num>
  <heading>Pub endorsement.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>An on-premises retailer's license, class C or D, may apply for one or more pub endorsements in accordance with § <cite path="§25-117">25-117</cite>, [§] <cite path="§25-124">25-124</cite>, or [§] <cite path="§25-125">25-125</cite>.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The minimum annual fees for a pub endorsement shall apply as follows:</text>
    <text>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>1 pub endorsement</td>
          <td>$5,000</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>2 pub endorsements</td>
          <td>$7,500</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>3 pub endorsements</td>
          <td>$9,000.</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </text>
  </para>
  <annotations>
    <annotation app="2020-02-21" doc="D.C. Law 23-54" eff="2020-02-21" path="§2|(a)|(4)" type="History"/>
  </annotations>
</section>
